timeline_data.body: Opened https://github.com/eclipse-openj9/openj9/issues/20567 for the previous comment, it seems a different issue.
There is an AIX core file saved, see https://github.ibm.com/runtimes/automation/issues/116#issuecomment-97015346 and let me know if you need help to get it.
AIX core files can be found under http://vmfarm.rtp.raleigh.ibm.com/etc/cores/tmp/

Has this occurred again recently? The other Harmony crashes that started on showing up on Nov 7 were fixed by this PR:
https://github.com/eclipse-openj9/openj9/pull/20763

That was merged in on Dec 9 and I was wondering if it might have fixed this one as well.
I haven't seen it, I'll go ahead and close.
